---
title: Cal Smart Mexi-Cali Tilapia Bowls with Warm Bulgur Salad and Baja Sauce
description: Lightly seasoned, roasted tilapia shine in this balanced bowl featuring zesty bulgur, spinach and tomatoes. A liberal drizzle of Baja sauce over top is the best way to enjoy this delicious dish!
